[vc_row css=”.vc_custom_1581597772628{margin-top: 55px !important;}”][vc_column offset=”vc_col-md-6″][vc_column_text css_animation=”bottom-to-top” css=”.vc_custom_1710413898502{padding-top: 30px !important;}”]

ASNU – Classic replacement injectors

[/vc_column_text]

[vc_column_text]

The ASNU Classic Replacement Injectors

[/vc_column_text]

[/vc_column][vc_column offset=”vc_col-md-6″][vc_single_image image=”2709″ img_size=”full”][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row custom_css_code=”LmdlbS1idXR0b24tc2l6ZS1tZWRpdW0lN0IlMEElMjAlMjAlMjAlMjBtaW4td2lkdGglM0EyMjdweCUzQiUwQSUyMCUyMCUyMCUyMG1hcmdpbiUzQTIwcHglM0IlMEElN0Q=”][vc_column]
[vc_column_text]

ASNU are just finalising the design & manufacture of replacement injectors for OE applications that use Bosch D-Jetronic injectors that are now no longer produced. This will keep historic vehicles on the road without the need to spend thousands on updating their fuel system and management. More information on this product range will be available very soon.

[/vc_column_text]

[/vc_column][/vc_row]
